snippet: "I think that volume of negativity has done enough damage,'' Newt Gingrich said.
abstract: "I think that volume of negativity has done enough damage,'' Newt Gingrich said.
lead_paragraph: WALFORD, Iowa -- Newt Gingrich has dusted off an old theme song: "Eye of the Tiger,'' whose lyric "just a man and his will to survive" pumped from speakers as his campaign bus rolled dramatically into the warehouse of an excavating company here.

headline.main: Gingrich Says He Is Unlikely to Win Iowa Caucus
